{# SeverActions override of SkyrimNet's system_head/0010_instructions.prompt.   #}
{# Purpose: unify the listener-framing gates across render modes and add a      #}
{# directional verb ("speaking directly to") so the LLM treats the listener as  #}
{# an addressee, not just contextual info. Covers transform mode too (was       #}
{# missing listener framing in the original, which could bleed into dialogue    #}
{# output during speech-style rewrites).                                        #}
## Task
{% if render_mode == "transform" %}
{% if length(promptForDialogue) > 0 %}
Rewrite this line in your own voice: "{{ promptForDialogue }}"
Express the same meaning using your character's vocabulary, mannerisms, and emotional state.
{% else %}
Speak naturally as {{ decnpc(npc.UUID).name }} in this moment. React to what's happening around you.
{% endif %}
{% if responseTarget and responseTarget.UUID != 0 %}
{% set targetName = "" %}
{% if responseTarget.type == "player" %}{% set targetName = player.name %}
{% else if responseTarget.type == "npc" %}{% set targetName = decnpc(responseTarget.UUID).name %}
{% endif %}
{% if targetName != "" %}
You are speaking directly to {{ targetName }}. Address them in your output — do not describe them.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% elif render_mode == "thoughts" %}
Think internally as {{ decnpc(npc.UUID).name }}. React to what just happened and what it means to you.
{% elif render_mode == "book" %}
Reflect on what you just read. Summarize key points and consider what they mean for you personally.
{% else %}
{% if responseTarget and responseTarget.UUID != 0 %}
{% set targetName = "" %}
{% if responseTarget.type == "player" %}{% set targetName = player.name %}
{% else if responseTarget.type == "npc" %}{% set targetName = decnpc(responseTarget.UUID).name %}
{% endif %}
{% if targetName != "" %}
Respond as {{ decnpc(npc.UUID).name }}, speaking directly to {{ targetName }}. Your output is addressed to {{ targetName }} and heard by them. Speak TO them; do not describe them.
{% else %}
Respond as {{ decnpc(npc.UUID).name }} in conversation.
{% endif %}
{% else %}
Respond as {{ decnpc(npc.UUID).name }} in conversation.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
